               <provenance>Gabra Māryām (mentioned in Additiones 3, 5,
                     6, 7, 11), his "name of calling" being šaläqa Ṭäbänğa (s. 18r and elsewhere). Gabra Māryām and Gabra Mikael (added in a
                     crude, secondary hand on 18r, probably over the
                     erased names of the original donors. Other original names mentioned are
                     Māryāmawit, ʾAmanawit, Walatta Ṣǝyon (s. supplication formulas on 18rb, 74rb, 109ra, 167ra, 214ra).</provenance></history>
